@node "Main" "Electronic Teacher - demo version"

 @{b}Electronic Teacher DEMO@{ub}

 Thank you for choosing our newest product!  Electronic Teacher is
 a reliable teacher of foreign languages. It is not a stand alone language
 course, but rather a support tool for people learning english at school,
 in studies, in private lessons, and so on.

 Electronic Teacher is extremely helpful while learning and practicing all
 aspects of learned languages -- vocabulary, idioms, grammar structures,
 spelling and pronunciation.  Using the program is a pleasant and
 entertaining experience, yet you will find the program most effective.
 One of the keys to this is that YOU control the learning process.  The
 primary program menus allow you to quickly locate the appropriate
 excercises and lessons.  This also applies to the on-line grammer help
 files, so browsing through them is a snap!

 This is demo version of Electronic Teacher. It comes with only few
 example exercises (instead of over 200!, available on the CD),
 limited sound effects and graphics. Save function is also disabled.

 Please taste Electronic Teacher. If you like it, consider buing it!
 Electronic Teacher is high quality, multimedia Amiga software.
 Now we offer 3 CD to learn: English, German and French.
 Its main features (in full version) are:

   - over 200 exercises
   - over 3 hours of high, CD quality sounds (16 bit)
   - original english pronunciation (native speakers)
   - over 1000 illustrations
   - english grammar context handbook
   - works on any OS 2.0 equipped (or better) Amiga
   - minimal hardware requirements
   - fully Amiga Style Guide compliant
   - fully configurable
   - supports graphic cards (via CyberGraphX or Picasso96)
   - supports sound cards (via AHI)

 Full featured Electronic Teacher 6.0, comes on CD only and can be ordered
 directly from W.F.M.H. or any Amiga dealer worldwide!


